Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED Kimi noooo hitooomi niiii utsutta boooku haaa}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:20.25,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnDay Roman\fs75\blur0.9\shad4\pos(650,515)\c&HF9FBFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H81&}Front Line Corp. NA Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoura here. What's your status?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're going to start charging now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.68,0:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be over soon, so bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your maintenance results show no irregularities in your control system or power supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems with your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really though, your every nook and cranny is {\i1}thoroughly{\i0} maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have a {\i1}caring{\i0} master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wonderful master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP HABATAKEEEE UTAGOE HA EEEENDOREEESU}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:43.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is endless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:50.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My eternal pledge is only for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:56.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wonder if you're your usual self
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:02.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll sparkle with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:15.29,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The arms of the clock advance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:21.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and with them so does time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:28.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}When you are sad, I open my tiny arms
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:35.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:43.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is tender
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:50.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I can remember your shape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and that wasn't brought about by a program
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Let us experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:02.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}the turmoil in my heart together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.96,Default,,0,170,0,,Ann still isn't done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something you can rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just read a magazine or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But places like this all have lame magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This article looks like it was made for you! {TS oh wait it's untranslatable}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"The forbidden putty buffing mod!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your bust will increase by 10 mm!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what the article says!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here's an article made for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Increases your calculation abilities!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,”Tuna Jellycan with DHA!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That does sound good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any longer and we would've rusted away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but there's one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to have X-rays done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They make you drink that Radiocontrast Jellycan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all white and gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, they've started using new fruit-flavored Jellycans that go down easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting cherry flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I wanna get a sip, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any reason to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with drinking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just a pain to deal with on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't have killed 'em to give your chaperones a checkup, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't manufactured by Front Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but if you just want to check sight, hearing, or voltage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you can use the self-diagnosis corner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that sounds like fun! I wanna try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way for your X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please refrain from vomiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll turn your power off for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be X-raying a sensitive area next,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a precaution against any unwanted problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, tuna, and then blow fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,cod, skipjack tuna, sillago, sea bream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how did the X-rays go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The detailed report has been sent directly to your master,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're all free to go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you doin' all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The maintenance left her a bit light-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She should return to normal soon enough, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your scheduled maintenance is now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That Nurse Shinki gave me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so angry, Ines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurses as aloof as her are popular with men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we look like men to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That receptionist nurse was way nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt. We must ask you to submit to a cavity search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This company is developing a new Shinki line, hence the heightened security.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't steal or anything like... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I just forgot to return it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooperate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not hear her say it was an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you wish to cross swords right here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You simply must be more careful, Ines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last person I want to hear that from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't help but wonder where she picked those lines up from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how long are you gonna swing that sword around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What kinda question's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lene, she's Ines—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leneshe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A Russian spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann's totally lost her marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it due to her maintenance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't have botched it {\i1}this{\i0} badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't take her back to Master like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we take her back for another checkup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Back to those Security Shinkis and that Nurse Shinki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing that here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier must keep her weapon in optimal condition for when it will be needed most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've replaced the data of that Shinki's AI unit with the new model's during maintenance and sent her outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is an Arnval model.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There should also be an Altines and Altlene model with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve her ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my X-rays?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps... you should go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Strarf that's under development!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bug in her AI, so watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch her so we can fix her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I slipped up and allowed the Strarf model escape the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Her AI is that of the Arnval's, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading toward your position immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is more convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the contents of both of their AI units.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch. Why would a BD release need an eyecatch?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're we doin' this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann was wielding those scary weapons a bit too seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and glared rather menacingly at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's sure gotten loud around here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, stop waving that thing around or you'll poke an eye out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where're ya goin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me, we need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A challenger wishing to do battle with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, I shall accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... that's my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your{\i0} body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up, Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Master will scold you if you pick a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know our names?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You nuts? Ann's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way I could make you believe that I'm Ann?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ann's right here, so probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines, your chest was actually a defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Master told me that it was 1 mm smaller than the normal Altines models.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew about it before he registered you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said to me, "it's not the size of the chest that matters."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, Lene!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was registered before you were, so I heard the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only ones who know about it are Master, me...{*13：22 がいrouは at the end? idk}{i dont understand your comment here, but the tl is corret}{このことを知っているのはマスターと私以外ではAnnさんだけ}{... Wow, not even I understand my comment here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So they turned you off during the X-ray examination,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you woke up, you found you were in a different Shinki's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means your minds must have been switched!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it explains why Ann started swingin' her sword around like a psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, what've you been all antsy about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This body was undergoing an X-ray examination, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you need to eject the photoreactive Jellycan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,why were the contents of our bodies exchanged?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever the reason, we know what happened now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all we need to do is just swap your AI unit data, and everything'll be back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we possibly do that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The AI unit is an essential component that governs a Shinki's emotions and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishandling it could cause the data to become irrecoverable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I could lose all the memories I have with Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If two people hold each other and fall down the stairs of a shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:53.37,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Rounded MT\fax0.25\blur0.95\b1\fs15\frz359\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H6E&\pos(568,472)}Body-Swapping Stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they can apparently switch bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You kiddin' me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, it is not something we should do lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We should return to the lab, explain the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and have them revert us to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You wandered pretty far out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Front Line doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to a handling error, we swapped your AI unit data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The lab has all the equipment needed to return you to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How the heck did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall explain the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll have to ask you two to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be a long distance, so why a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's so we can get our hands on the AI unit filled with Front Line's latest technological secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the Shinki model they developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew something was weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's no Front Line Shinki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,inside a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses, I was careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't switch back soon, Master will worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're going to Japan in a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where my master was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lived in America a long time due to his father's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's going back to Japan for high school. {Oooooh, so this is a prequel episode.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines, Lene and I are all going with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we absolutely must return to Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been shipped out yet, so you still don't have a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am programmed only to serve my master absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is a "master"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My master...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is kind, but still a bit clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves us all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should have a photo of him in my memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He is... your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're bustin' you out, Ann!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me! {lol traffic violations}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You will not intervene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One move, and I'll pierce her AI unit. {That is one lewd Shinki. A+}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now discard your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I said now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't care about this girl's precious memories of her master, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that AI unit out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing sick won't fool me. {literally fart powers}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then, we'll return the AI units to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In the interest of protecting trade secrets, we'll need to erase the memories you had while in each other's bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we only just became friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not remember such an occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough that we're able to return them to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, incidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you both saw and heard plenty of things you shouldn't have,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll need to erase a bit of your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, we're beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever happen to meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make such promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we could meet again, we wouldn't remember each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of your kind master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find a wonderful master too, Strarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job picking out the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The cherry-flavored photoreactive fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, I don't remember you getting maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, you've been kinda weird since you got reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been reset,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but perhaps it was the events of that day that brought my memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.60,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The day may come when you will remember it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez Master, you're late again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find a good dumpling shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We already have plenty of dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is good that we could all meet again this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,With Master as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's up? Talking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lene, don't drink the Nitro Jellycan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awwright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:26.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I stand here reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:31.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and make something of a foolish face
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:39.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Being more gentle than the wind and invincible like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:44.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:51.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Here in the forest I am lost in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:57.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to try finding a four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:24:04.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The sun is guiding me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:10.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}towards the miracles of two stars together
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:13.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Even if we are hurt on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.64,0:24:17.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and ten years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:24.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}this future where I can be with you is what I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:25.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will walk on ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:30.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not miss the sun's sign
